name: Space Shuttle Series – Discovery
description:
Update 16/10/13:
Discovery is now available to purchase. Celebrating 30 years of the NASA Space Shuttle Program. The second in this series of Space Shuttle prints is dedicated to NASA's third Shuttle, Discovery. Hand pulled silkscreen - 420mm x 594mm Lascaux Studio Bronze/custom mix - "Champagne Supernova" GF Smith Black Plike – 240gsm Print comes wrapped in acid free tissue paper and sealed in a cardboard poster tube. This print is limited to a hand numbered edition of 100. 71 Beautifully screen printed by Dan Mather
